OL,3,CWater boss admits 'devastating' impact
OL,4,Cof parasite outbreak while pay rises
OL,6,FThe boss of South West Water's owner
OL,7,Fhas apologised to customers over
OL,8,Fpollution incidents, including the
OL,9,F"devastating" parasite outbreak in
OL,10,FDevon, while revealing her salary has
OL,11,Frisen this year.
OL,13,FPennon, which also owns supplier SES
OL,14,FWater, has come under fire for rising
OL,15,Fcases of sewage spills affecting
OL,16,Fcustomers and the environment.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@MO]
