OL,3,CWater boss admits 'devastating' impact
OL,4,Cof parasite outbreak while pay rises
OL,6,FChief executive Susan Davy, speaking
OL,7,Fto a group of MPs on the cross-party
OL,8,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,9,FCommittee, admitted that "things do go
OL,10,Fwrong" for the utilities giant.
OL,12,F"I absolutely regret and do not
OL,13,Fcondone those incidents and pollutions
OL,14,Fthat we had.
OL,16,F"We do not want to harm the
OL,17,Fenvironment, that is not the
OL,18,Factivities that we undertake every day.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@FO]tD@AOUxD@AOU
