OL,3,CWater boss admits 'devastating' impact
OL,4,Cof parasite outbreak while pay rises
OL,6,F"We have hundreds of treatment works
OL,7,Fand thousands of pumping stations and
OL,8,Ffrom time to time things do go wrong."
OL,10,FPollution incidents at South West
OL,11,FWater ` which serves about 1.8 million
OL,12,Fcustomers in Cornwall, Devon and parts
OL,13,Fof Somerset and Dorset ` soared by 80%
OL,14,Fto 194 between 2023 and 2024.
OL,16,FPennon was fined #2.2 million in 2023
OL,17,Ffor illegal sewage spills spanning
OL,18,Ffour years across Devon and Cornwall.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@fO]
