OL,3,CWater boss admits 'devastating' impact
OL,4,Cof parasite outbreak while pay rises
OL,6,FMs Davy told the committee that the
OL,7,Fcompany has changed how it checks for
OL,8,Fwater contamination since the crisis
OL,9,Fin Brixham, Devon, last year.
OL,11,FThe outbreak last May left some people
OL,12,Fin hospital and hundreds of others ill
OL,13,Fafter contamination of the water
OL,14,Fsupply by cryptosporidium, a parasite
OL,15,Fwhich causes sickness and diarrhoea.
OL,17,F"I absolutely understand how
OL,18,Fdevastating that incident was for that
OL,19,Fcommunity and for the customers who
OL,20,Fwere poorly... it was a really
OL,21,Fhorrible time for them," she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@XO]
