OL,3,CWater boss admits 'devastating' impact
OL,4,Cof parasite outbreak while pay rises
OL,6,F"I am always sorry when something
OL,7,Fhappens whether to our customers or to
OL,8,Fthe environment."
OL,10,FPennon faced some criticism after
OL,11,Fannouncing in June, following the
OL,12,Fincident, that Ms Davy's pay package
OL,13,Fjumped 58% to #860,000 in 2023-24,
OL,14,Fafter she picked up a long-term share
OL,15,Faward.
OL,17,FShe also told the committee that her
OL,18,Fbase salary was rising from #494,000
OL,19,Fto #511,000 this year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]
