OL,3,CWater boss admits 'devastating' impact
OL,4,Cof parasite outbreak while pay rises
OL,6,FShe insisted that she does not set her
OL,7,Fown pay ` that is the responsibility
OL,8,Fof the company's remuneration
OL,9,Fcommittee ` but admitted she was "well
OL,10,Fpaid for what is a very responsible
OL,11,Fand accountable role".
OL,13,F"I've had a history of not taking
OL,14,Fannual bonuses ` I didn't take it last
OL,15,Fyear for the cryptosporidium
OL,16,Foutbreak," she added.
OL,26,@qD@bOUsD@UO]uD@AOUxD@JO]
